            <p><strong>Debug Info for /{lang}:</strong></p>
            <p>Found Data: {foundData ? "Yes" : "No"}</p>
            <p>Language Filter: {languageFilter}</p>
            <p>Title: {heroTitle || "None"}</p>
            <p>Subtitle: {heroSubtitle || "None"}</p>
            <p>Image: {heroImgUrl || "None"}</p>
